[genericglass Collins] Serving Glass: Collins With Ice

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
1 1/2 oz [genericingredient Scotch] Glenlivet Scotch Whiskey
1/2 oz Drambuie
2 oz [genericingredient Lemon Juice] Lemon Juice
1 tsp Powder Sugar
Shake and Strain
Top: Club Soda
Garnish: Cherry
Garnish: Orange Slice

